Title: The Secret Life of the Dipole
Author: Jeeva S. Anandan
Comments: 6 pages, latex. A shorter version of this article, but with two
  figures, appeared in Nature, vol. 387, 558-559 (5 June 1997)
\\
  A new force on the magnetic dipole, which exists in the presence of both
electric and magnetic fields, is described. Its origin due to the `hidden
momentum', implications and possible experimental tests are discussed.
